What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's your senior essay. You have to do it. Start early!
You have to take it to graduate, but it's worth it!
A lot of hard work, needs a lot of preparation. Such a good academic process to strengthen research and writing skills.
Find a wonderful adviser, find a topic you love, try your best to do little chunks throughout the year, and you'll be golden. It can be a really enjoyable experience, I promise!
